Package: RfastHPOCR
Type: Package
Title: R Bindings to 'FastHPOCR' Phenotype Concept Recognition
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person(given = "Sounkou Mahamane", family = "Toure",
           email = "sounkoutoure@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person(given = "Tudor", family = "Groza", role = c("ctb", "cph"),
           comment = "Author and copyright holder of the upstream 'FastHPOCR' Python package")
    )
Description: R bindings to the 'FastHPOCR' Python package
    <https://github.com/tudorgroza/fast_hpo_cr> for fast phenotype concept
    recognition over Human Phenotype Ontology terms in free text. The package
    exposes reticulate-backed helpers for building ontology indexes and for
    annotating text with R-friendly data-frame outputs while preserving access
    to the underlying Python objects when needed.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/sounkou-bioinfo/RfastHPOCR,
    https://github.com/tudorgroza/fast_hpo_cr
BugReports: https://github.com/sounkou-bioinfo/RfastHPOCR/issues
SystemRequirements: Python (>= 3.8); Python packages FastHPOCR, pronto, and tqdm
Encoding: UTF-8
